{"tid":531278,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【SR-72】波音不甘勢弱，研發新黑鳥，俄中防空全廢","createTime":"2018-01-16T15:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T07:54:19.000Z","uid":147314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5e5d2a663386061ad84bf8de1d50c1ba76ceeb5e","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-01-14/656/20180114003006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-01-14%2F656%2F20180114003006.jpg&h=9b40c3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不讓洛馬專美於前，波音也要研發極超音速飛機，以競爭黑鳥之子的名號。(圖/波音公司)<br />\n<br />\nSR-71黑鳥(Black Bird)3倍音速偵察機家喻戶曉，它是洛克希德公司(Lockheed )在1960年代創造的，長年穩坐「最快速飛機」的王座，然而它已退役很多年，近年美國空軍又提出高空高速戰略偵察機的研發計畫，為此洛馬公司(Lockheed Martin)推動SR-72，並且正在研發中。然而波音公司(Boeing)也不甘勢弱，在本周首次展示了5馬赫極超音速飛機的概念模型，競爭誰才夠資格成為「黑鳥之子」。<br />\n<br />\n大眾機械(popular mechanics)報導，波音版本的黑鳥之子還處於未批准全面開發的早期概念階段，而它的外型也很類似洛馬提出的SR-72，不過改成雙垂尾與複合式三角翼(類似過去的太空梭)，波音公司高超音速研究負責人，首席超音速科學家凱文．波庫特(Kevin Bowcutt)說：「我們公司內部自己做了一個獨立的研究部門來推進這項計畫，假如有所收穫應該就可以列為全面發展項目。目前會先從一架F-16那般大的前驅驗證機開始，要是一切順利，就會以此基礎製作一架雙發動機，32公尺長的大型版，大約與過去的SR-71黑鳥差不多。"},{"pid":"d3ec2a033297f55f9328e9544482b520a1a76a78","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTNCUutX0AAjHbu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTNCUutX0AAjHbu.jpg&h=5ae60c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n波音公司過去很長時間都有研發極超音速概念飛機，也就是X-43和X-51乘波 (Waverider)實驗機，都曾飛到6馬赫以上，其中X-51曾經打破了「進氣飛行器超音速飛行的記錄」，當時它以5.1馬赫飛行三分半鐘，然後在2013年5月1日耗盡燃料落入太平洋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-01-14/656/20180114003008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-01-14%2F656%2F20180114003008.jpg&h=8ecad1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNASA與波音在2000年前後曾研究過X-43與X-51，是他們研究極超音速飛行的技術基礎。(圖/NASA)<br />\n<br />\n然而，不管X-43或是X-51，他們體積都非常小(長3.65 公尺，寛1.5公尺)，而且飛行的初始速度來自外力，首先它們是由B-52轟炸機搭載，然後機體後方安裝一具助推用的飛馬座火箭，先是從B-52在高速時抛擲下來，點燃飛馬座火箭達到5馬赫，再使用極衝壓發動機保持或是加速。至於可實用化的極超音速飛機必須從靜止起飛，在高空加速到5馬赫以上，還可以減速並安然降落，這是一個更困難的挑戰。"},{"pid":"b4d4793ed304b4b263e42ab99ab40a12180a85e7","tid":531278,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"波音股價已贏"},{"pid":"981d31d31a551eaad952349a36b32fd95952908c","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-01-14/656/20180114003013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-01-14%2F656%2F20180114003013.jpg&h=c4dbd9c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洛馬的SR-72與波音的極超音速概念，最大差別在垂尾的設計，波音是雙尾的，洛馬是單尾的。(圖/洛馬公司)<br />\n<br />\n為了解決這個問題，波音和洛馬都知道，極超音速飛機必須有兩種分別不同特性的引擎，一種是中低速的渦輪扇發動機，負責低速到3馬赫的飛行模式，另一種超過3馬赫時點燃的衝壓/超燃衝壓發動機，這稱為渦輪聯合循環式發動機（TBCC）， 這種發動機的概念在30年前就已提出，但是對於高溫高壓的冶金要求極高，因此直到現在，這些航空大廠才敢再次挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180114002997-260417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180114002997-260417&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyu4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=297d419c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180114002997-260417</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Son of Blackbird&quot;: Boeing Reveals Hypersonic Concept That Could Replace SR-71<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.popularmechanics.com/military/aviation/a15070935/boeing-hypersonic-concept-replace-sr-71-blackbird/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popularmechanics.com%2Fmilitary%2Faviation%2Fa15070935%2Fboeing-hypersonic-concept-replace-sr-71-blackbird%2F&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyu4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=2e31b013\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.popularmechanics.com/military/aviation/a15070935/boeing-hypersonic-concept-replace-sr-71-blackbird/</a>"},{"pid":"6dc4b1fb7803d614b94f1372116d1a291e149ff1","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"6馬赫神速！美「黑鳥」之子無人偵察機出世<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-01-10/656/20180110002934.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-01-10%2F656%2F20180110002934.jpg&h=a59ee80b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國SR-72高超音速戰略偵察機的示意圖。（洛克希德馬丁）"},{"pid":"6f10a5a47dac2d76da25d495c58589c345673366","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"洛克希德馬丁（Lockheed Martin）旗下的「臭鼬工廠」（Skunk Works）很可能已完成SR-72原型，以取代SR-71「黑鳥」（Blackbird）偵察機。SR-72的速度號稱可達6馬赫，為SR-7偵察機的兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n洛馬戰略與顧客要求先進開發專案（Strategy and Customer Requirements, Advanced Development Programs）副總裁歐巴尼恩（Jack O&rsquo;Banion）在一場論壇中，意外透露了「黑鳥」之子出世的消息。<br />\n<br />\n他在美國航太科學技術研究院論壇（The American Institute of Aeronautics and Astronautics SciTech Forum）中，展示了SR-72的數位模型，並說：「要是沒有數位轉型（digital transformation），不可能造出各位所看到的這架飛機。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTC2WtYW4AEK0rt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTC2WtYW4AEK0rt.jpg&h=53581267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a05756e30a6c69b8ab977386151deb01742946a","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"他甚至表示：「事實上，5年前它是不可能打造出來的。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，歐巴尼恩說，SR-72會有架對它瞭如指掌的「數位雙胞胎」。他並指出，SR-72的速度會達超過5馬赫的高超音速。<br />\n<br />\n據《航太周刊》（Aviation Week）去年底報導，有人看到，一架據信是SR-72的小型無人驗證機7月時飛入美國空軍的加州棕櫚谷（Palmdale）42廠（Plant 42），也就是「臭鼬工廠」的總部。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，自2000年代初以來，洛馬就在研發SR-72高超音速飛機。洛馬高層先前透露，SR-72的研發將整合「聯合循環發動機」（combined cycle engine），以及其他高超音速飛行相關技術，著手打造約為F-22戰機大小的展示機。<br />\n<br />\n而聯合循環推進系統結合了渦輪機與衝壓噴射發動機，得以將飛機從靜止狀態，瞬間把速度推升到5馬赫以上。"},{"pid":"18755fe4d0ef3a6e8542b1c8802c3989bc2e563c","tid":531278,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"有衛星仲要呢類野做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a66088f678ae10b818a637ba1c0d2b2a53ce8a1","tid":531278,"uid":9564,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"唔係叫署光女神咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5b6687f5191b2bfb40765c8800cdae29b08ca6","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18755fe4d0ef3a6e8542b1c8802c3989bc2e563c","tid":531278,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"有衛星仲要呢類野做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"部機可以攻擊架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee765842c5612a869572bf91d98f1359b1231db","tid":531278,"uid":34666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18755fe4d0ef3a6e8542b1c8802c3989bc2e563c","tid":531278,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"有衛星仲要呢類野做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"大部份衛星只可以行固定軌道, 唔可以提供實時影像"},{"pid":"c11c0a37175476ac5947adc9886d3f240119343a","tid":531278,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5b6687f5191b2bfb40765c8800cdae29b08ca6","tid":531278,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18755fe4d0ef3a6e8542b1c8802c3989bc2e563c","tid":531278,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"有衛星仲要呢類野做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"部機可以攻擊架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"有彈道導彈喎"},{"pid":"0549ad12262ae235ba53a305760141f97f093470","tid":53